math.randomseed(tick()); math.random()
local Tool = script.Parent local Handle = Tool.Handle
local ProjectileScript
local myCharacter local myHumanoid
local ServeAnim
function onActivated() if not Tool.Enabled then return end ProjectileScript = Tool:FindFirstChild("VolleyballProjScript") if ProjectileScript then Tool.Enabled = false myCharacter = Tool.Parent myHumanoid = myCharacter:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") if myHumanoid then ServeAnim = Tool:FindFirstChild("VolleyballServe") if ServeAnim then ServeAnim = myHumanoid:LoadAnimation(ServeAnim) ServeAnim:Play() end end local CloneScript = ProjectileScript:Clone() CloneScript.Parent = Tool CloneScript.Disabled = false wait(1.2) if Handle:FindFirstChild("HitSound") then Handle.HitSound:Play() end Handle.Transparency = 1.0 wait(3.9) Handle.Transparency = 0.0 Tool.Enabled = true end end
function onEquipped() if not Tool.Enabled then wait(3) Tool.Enabled = true end end
function onUnequipped() if ServeAnim then ServeAnim:Stop() end Handle.Transparency = 0.0 end
Tool.Activated:connect(onActivated) Tool.Equipped:connect(onEquipped) Tool.Unequipped:connect(onUnequipped)

function waitForChild(parent, childName) while not parent:FindFirstChild(childName) do parent.ChildAdded:wait() end return parent[childName] end
local ScreenGui = waitForChild(script, "VolleyballScreenGui")
local PlayerList = game.Players:GetChildren()
function addGuiToPlayer(Player) if Player:FindFirstChild("VolleyballScreenGui") then return end if not Player:FindFirstChild("WantsToPlayVolleyball") then
local GuiClone = ScreenGui:Clone() GuiClone.Parent = waitForChild(Player, "PlayerGui") waitForChild(GuiClone, "VolleyballPlayerScript").Disabled = false
elseif Player.WantsToPlayVolleyball.Value == true then
local GuiClone = ScreenGui:Clone() GuiClone.Parent = waitForChild(Player, "PlayerGui") waitForChild(GuiClone, "VolleyballPlayerScript").Disabled = false end end
function addGuiToCharacter(char) addGuiToPlayer(game.Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(char)) end
for index, Player in pairs(PlayerList) do addGuiToPlayer(Player) end
game.Players.PlayerAdded:connect(function(Player) Player.CharacterAdded:connect(addGuiToCharacter) end)

myPlayer = ScreenGui.Parent.Parent if myPlayer:FindFirstChild("WantsToPlayVolleyball") then wantsToPlay() else NoButton.MouseButton1Click:connect(doesntWantToPlay) YesButton.MouseButton1Click:connect(wantsToPlay) end
